WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.120 --> 00:00:02.100
Third uncle fight

2
00:00:04.800 --> 00:00:06.680
If the emperor is angry, he can speak directly

3
00:00:06.680 --> 00:00:09.780
But don't bully me, a patient who has just been detoxified and has not yet recovered.

4
00:00:10.920 --> 00:00:13.600
I see you are recovering very well now.

5
00:00:13.600 --> 00:00:18.060
That can't resist the emperor's sour and angry vinegar jar smashing down

6
00:00:18.600 --> 00:00:19.860
Why are you in Bailing County?

7
00:00:20.400 --> 00:00:21.820
The minister came again and again

8
00:00:22.640 --> 00:00:24.220
Is to clear up the misunderstanding

9
00:00:33.520 --> 00:00:35.560
The antidote that Empress developed for me is very effective

10
00:00:35.560 --> 00:00:37.500
The minister originally planned to return to the fief to worship

11
00:00:37.600 --> 00:00:40.060
Passing through this plague land on the way back

12
00:00:40.120 --> 00:00:42.620
I saw the empress being bullied by that bad official

13
00:00:42.680 --> 00:00:44.060
That's why I'm helping

14
00:00:44.280 --> 00:00:46.740
As for why now I only call him Empress

15
00:00:46.920 --> 00:00:49.700
Because he is just your Shen Xingyao now

16
00:00:50.080 --> 00:00:51.620
Instead of my Yao'er

17
00:00:53.320 --> 00:00:54.220
What do you mean?

18
00:00:54.240 --> 00:00:55.300
According to the minister

19
00:00:55.320 --> 00:00:57.220
Yao Er hit his head before marriage

20
00:00:57.640 --> 00:00:59.420
She's been in tears ever since.

21
00:00:59.440 --> 00:01:01.380
How can you stand the days of the cold palace?

22
00:01:01.440 --> 00:01:05.540
Jin Se once died because of Yao Er's serious illness and sought help from the eunuch in the palace

23
00:01:05.720 --> 00:01:07.540
And there was no one.

24
00:01:08.880 --> 00:01:10.140
But since then

25
00:01:10.200 --> 00:01:11.940
Yao Er suddenly recovered

26
00:01:12.080 --> 00:01:13.740
Even personality changes

27
00:01:14.080 --> 00:01:16.220
Shouldn't say

28
00:01:16.640 --> 00:01:18.400
It's like a different person

29
00:01:18.400 --> 00:01:19.600
I don't want to believe it either

30
00:01:19.600 --> 00:01:22.440
Until rescuing others with the Empress in Bailing County

31
00:01:22.440 --> 00:01:23.580
Have to admit

32
00:01:23.680 --> 00:01:25.500
He is not the daughter of the Shen family for a long time

33
00:01:26.040 --> 00:01:28.900
Why are you so sure he's not?

34
00:01:29.680 --> 00:01:33.380
A woman who would rather die than get married

35
00:01:33.440 --> 00:01:37.300
How could you go to that plague land to save your people for the emperor?

36
00:01:37.480 --> 00:01:40.060
Since he can love the emperor with all his heart

37
00:01:40.160 --> 00:01:42.220
That's not the one I love

38
00:01:44.600 --> 00:01:46.940
The Prime Minister Shen's mansion suffered

39
00:01:47.000 --> 00:01:49.900
It is the scourge of the Zhenguo General's Mansion seizing power

40
00:01:50.040 --> 00:01:52.380
The minister is willing to cooperate with the emperor to investigate the evidence

41
00:01:52.880 --> 00:01:55.700
Send me Qin Guodong to end

42
00:01:56.400 --> 00:01:57.400
As for Yao'er

43
00:01:57.400 --> 00:01:59.020
It's the blessing of my life

44
00:01:59.720 --> 00:02:01.420
It's the regret of my life

45
00:02:01.680 --> 00:02:04.860
His departure may have been a profound disappointment in the world

46
00:02:05.000 --> 00:02:09.580
Including me who guarded the border and couldn't get back to the capital in time

47
00:02:11.680 --> 00:02:16.260
I implore the emperor to take the guzheng that Yao'er married when she entered the palace

48
00:02:16.680 --> 00:02:17.860
Return to minister

49
00:02:20.360 --> 00:02:21.160
OK

50
00:02:21.960 --> 00:02:22.900
Looking for it?

